videos.headline: Whitlow gets Auburn on the board with a TD

videos.description: Auburn's Kam Martin goes right through the defense for the easy 35-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Martin goes untouched for the Auburn TD) 2019/09/14

videos.headline: Whitlow cruises into the end zone for the Auburn TD

videos.headline: Auburn runs flea-flicker to perfection
videos.description: Auburn runs the flea-flicker and it leads to a wide-open Eli Stove who scores the touchdown.
